<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ١٣ ... سُورَةُ الرَّعْدِ ... آياتها ٤٣ ... مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَوَى عَلَى الْعَرْشِ}</span> ... عَلَا وَارْتَفَعَ وَاسْتَقَرَّ، كَمَا يَلِيقُ بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ}</span> ... جِبَالًا تُثَبِّتُ الأَرْضَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُغْشِي}</span> ... يُغَطِّي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قِطَعٌ}</span> ... بِقَاعٌ مُخْتَلِفَةٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّتَجَاوِرَاتٌ}</span> ... يُجَاوِرُ بَعْضُهَا بَعْضًا،<span class="c5"> مِنْهَا:</span> طَيِّبَةٌ،<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهَا:</span> سَبِخَةٌ مَلِحَةٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَنَخِيلٌ صِنْوَانٌ}</span> ... مُجْتَمِعَةٌ فِي مَنْبَتٍ وَاحِدٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الأَغْلَالُ}</span> ... السَّلَاسِلُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَثُلَاتُ}</span> ... عُقُوبَاتُ أَمْثَالِهِمْ مِنَ المُكَذِّبِينَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَغِيضُ الأَرْحَامُ}</span> ... تَنْقُصُهُ الأَرْحَامُ؛ فَيَسْقُطُ قَبْلَ تَمَامِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُتَعَالِ}</span> ... العَالِي بِذَاتِهِ وَقَدْرِهِ وَقَهْرِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَارِبٌ}</span> ... مَنْ جَهَرَ بِأَعْمَالِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُعَقِّبَاتٌ}</span> ... مَلَائِكَةٌ يَتَعَاقَبُونَ عَلَى الإِنْسَانِ لِحِفْظِهِ، وَإِحْصَاءِ عَمَلِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن وَالٍ}</span> ... وَلِيٍّ يَتَوَلَّى أُمُورَهُمْ، وَيَدْفَعُ البَلَاءَ عَنْهُمْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>